extends layout

block content
  div(class="min-h-screen flex flex-col")
    //- Header
    header(class="border-b border-gray-700 h-16 flex items-center px-6")
      div(class="max-w-4xl mx-auto w-full")
        a(href="/" class="font-semibold text-sm tracking-tight flex items-center gap-2")
          span(class="text-lg") ▲
          span InviteChat

    //- Main
    main(class="flex-1 py-16 px-6")
      div(class="max-w-2xl mx-auto")
        div(class="mb-12")
          p(class="text-gray-500 text-xs font-mono mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider") legal
          h1(class="text-2xl font-medium") Terms of Service
          p(class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-2") Last updated: January 2026
        
        div(class="space-y-10 text-sm text-gray-300 leading-relaxed")
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 01
              | Acceptance of Terms
            p By accessing and using InviteChat services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree to these terms, please do not use our services.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 02
              | Description of Service
            p InviteChat provides premium community access through Discord and Telegram. Upon successful payment and account connection, users receive access to premium features and private channels.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 03
              | Payment and Refunds
            p All payments are processed securely through Stripe. Payments are non-refundable except in cases of technical issues preventing service delivery. Contact us within 7 days of purchase if you experience any issues.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 04
              | User Conduct
            p Users must comply with Discord and Telegram Terms of Service and Community Guidelines. We reserve the right to revoke premium access for users who violate community standards or engage in harmful behavior.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 05
              | Account Security
            p You are responsible for maintaining the security of your accounts. We are not liable for any loss or damage arising from unauthorized access to your account.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 06
              | Modifications to Service
            p We reserve the right to modify or discontinue the service at any time. We will provide reasonable notice of any significant changes.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 07
              | Limitation of Liability
            p InviteChat is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind. We are not liable for any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages.
          
          section
            h2(class="text-white font-medium mb-3 flex items-center gap-3")
              span(class="text-gray-500 font-mono text-xs") 08
              | Contact
            p For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us through our Discord server.
        
        div(class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-gray-700")
          a(href="/" class="text-gray-500 text-sm hover:text-white transition-colors") ← Back
